      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of picture caption with May 12 article; bishops shown backed demonstrators opposing United Methodist Church votes against ordination of active gays and against blessing of same-sex unions</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture caption in some copies on May 12 with an article about the United Methodist Church meeting in Cleveland, where leaders affirmed opposition to the ordination of active gays and to the blessing of same-sex unions, referred imprecisely to a group singing ''We Shall Overcome.'' The singers were bishops who supported demonstrators against the votes; they were not themselves demonstrators.</p>
      </block>
